{"TopicId":147430,"ForumId":70,"TopicTitle":"Ladder Troll Physics","CreatedByName":"MaxL_1023","CreatedById":152317,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T03:16:41Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"MaxL_1023","CreatedById":152317,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T03:16:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen a Kerbal climbs a ladder and runs into any obstacle (like a lander can sticking out 20cm from the ladder) climbing into the blockage will cause the entire ship to rotate about its center of mass, including the Kerbal which should be pushed the other way as opposed to turning with it.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBasically, a ladder can be used as a torque source by having a Kerbal climbing on it.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs this known?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am using \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Real Solar System (mod)\u0022\u003ERSS\u003C/abbr\u003E/RP-0 if it makes a difference.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stargate525","CreatedById":53585,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T06:11:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222750521\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022147430\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473563801\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152317\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MaxL_1023\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, MaxL_1023 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen a Kerbal climbs a ladder and runs into any obstacle (like a lander can sticking out 20cm from the ladder) climbing into the blockage will cause the entire ship to rotate about its center of mass, including the Kerbal which should be pushed the other way as opposed to turning with it.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBasically, a ladder can be used as a torque source by having a Kerbal climbing on it.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs this known?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am using \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Real Solar System (mod)\u0022\u003ERSS\u003C/abbr\u003E/RP-0 if it makes a difference.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes it is. It\u0027s not torque; it\u0027s a force. If you design it right, you can build a \u0027spaceship\u0027 that a kerbal can literally CLIMB to orbit with.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Chemp","CreatedById":154483,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T12:35:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222750521\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022147430\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473563801\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152317\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MaxL_1023\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, MaxL_1023 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs this known?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr you can do that: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/130865-bill-pedals-around-kerbin\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EBill pedals around Kerbin\u003C/a\u003E. In fact, there\u0027s even a \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/129062-105-kerbal-powered-flight/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Echallenge\u003C/a\u003E from \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/69507-geschosskopf/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002269507\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/69507-geschosskopf/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Geschosskopf\u003C/a\u003E that takes advantage of this \u003Cs\u003Eglitch\u003C/s\u003E feature. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaxL_1023","CreatedById":152317,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-12T01:18:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk, thanks guys. I flipped a couple landers and was wondering what was up.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-12T02:43:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222750521\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022147430\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473563801\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152317\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MaxL_1023\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n23 hours ago, MaxL_1023 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBasically, a ladder can be used as a torque source by having a Kerbal climbing on it.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs this known?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe KSP Ladder-Drive, the most fuel-efficient engine in the game, driving Kerbal expansion over the solar system since v0.18. A video showing it in action:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/8EZWbF3sQQI?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaxL_1023","CreatedById":152317,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-12T03:00:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf I was better at that kind of engineering I would try and use it to get into orbit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}